name: Fun T-Shirt Letters
description:
Create your very own t-shirt transfer! Just iron it onto your shirt or even a canvas bag!

Perhaps you have a favorite saying, or a nickname or perhaps you have a favourite picture.

Check out our list of fun fonts from our FONTS page and select one.

Depending in the font you select or the image you upload, the final image or text:
Height: will not exceed 4 inches
Width: will not exceed 4 inches
Colour: Black
Price per unit of Letter/symbol (eg !, ' ): $5.00/unit

For example: McDonald's equals: 10 units. 

Fonts are not owned by Stick It On. 

****COUNT UNITS AND ENTER QUANTITY IN THE QTY BOX. TELL US YOUR LETTERING IN THE COMMENTS BOX OR EMAIL THE IMAGE TO christine@carouselstationery.com.au****
